WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.189
The Platanus Hack 25 experience begins.

00:00:03.189 --> 00:00:05.799
We will welcome 200 hackers from Singapore,

00:00:05.799 --> 00:00:12.589
Argentina, Colombia, Guatemala, Peru, Mexico and Chile at Buk's offices to hack

00:00:12.599 --> 00:00:17.100
for 36 hours in one of the most ambitious hackathons in Latin America.

00:00:17.100 --> 00:00:20.600
Welcome to Platanus Hack 25.

00:00:20.600 --> 00:00:25.420
We are super excited to have 200 people with 200 hackers.

00:00:25.420 --> 00:00:29.879
At Buk we have a deep commitment to technology and innovation throughout Latin America.

00:00:29.879 --> 00:00:35.520
That's why we are very happy to create this space at Platanus Hack ft. Buk where probably

00:00:35.520 --> 00:00:39.420
the future founders and CTOs who will impact the tech ecosystem of tomorrow will emerge.

00:00:39.420 --> 00:00:43.060
It's been incredible.

00:00:43.060 --> 00:00:45.299
The people here are top tier.

00:00:45.299 --> 00:00:47.100
Every idea, every project that

00:00:47.100 --> 00:00:51.659
is born here is like a small spark for a big idea.

00:00:51.659 --> 00:00:54.439
We've been hacking for 17 hours now. On average

00:00:54.439 --> 00:00:59.759
two hours of sleep and I'm seeing the projects starting to take shape and we are very

00:01:00.100 --> 00:01:05.400
eager in the team to see what will come out of this in 17 more hours on Sunday

00:01:09.239 --> 00:01:11.230
Thank you!